==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bluing
<hw>Blu"ing</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
of rendering blue; <as>as, the <ex>bluing</ex> of steel</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Tomlinson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Something, as indigo or other preparations, used to
give a bluish tint, especially to white clothing when being
washed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bluish</ent>⟦br⟧
